column31:
If you join with SSCE it will be hard to be converted especially when your degree and NYSC will likely come after your appointment. 

Conversion happens when you have study leave approval from the Board or when you mistakenly or deliberately are placed wrongly. 

NYSC corpers that about to graduate can take chance but students dont need to rush. Yours will come at the right time. 

Dont kill your career before you even start.

Short story, guys!

So in my lodge, we're 4 corpers(all female)
3 yoruba and a hausa babe
So I noticed that one of us(yoruba) tries to bully the hausa babe.....whenever we have conversations and the hausa babe contributes to it, she'd just find a way to shut her up with the phrase 'you be hausa nau, you no fit understand ' amongst other silly comments. 

So this morning, while the hausa babe was trying to prepare for cds, she brought out her spray, and the yoruba babe stopped her from using it
She said, and I quote 'xxxx, please use the spray outside,  it smells mallam mallam and I don't like it'.... Brethren, it was really annoying and embarrassing, plus the spray is an OUD fragrance🥹🥹🥹

Soooooooooo guyyyysssss............
From tomorrow, I'll start smelling mallam mallam, too❤️
I hate bullies!!!!
